OL,3,CFans handed banning orders after
OL,4,Cdisorder at football match
OL,6,FThree men have been handed football
OL,7,Fbanning orders after they invaded the
OL,8,Fpitch during a match, and one
OL,9,Fassaulted a player.
OL,11,FThe fans entered the pitch from the
OL,12,Faway end when the Spirerites were
OL,13,Fplaying Oldham at the SMH Group
OL,14,FStadium on 19 August 2023.
OL,16,FReece Taylor, 28, of Hogarth Rise,
OL,17,FOldham, and Garry Morris, 42, of Edwin
OL,18,FAvenue, Chesterfield pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Fpublic order offences and were given
OL,20,Fthree-year banning orders and fines.
