OL,6,FAdam Carter, 34, of Sunnyside Road,
OL,7,FDroyslden, Manchester pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto assaulting a player on the pitch
OL,9,Fand was given a three-year banning
OL,10,Forder and a #1477 fine.
OL,12,FDedicated Football Officer at
OL,13,FDerbyshire Police PC Adam Collins
OL,14,Fsaid: "The behaviour of these
OL,15,Fsupporters was completely unacceptable
OL,16,Fand ruins the experience for thousands
OL,17,Fof football fans who come to enjoy
OL,18,Fgames in Chesterfield each season.
