OL,3,CFans handed banning orders after
OL,4,Cdisorder at football match
OL,6,F"As we approach a fixture at Boundary
OL,7,FPark this Saturday, I am sure both
OL,8,Fhome and away supporters will welcome
OL,9,Fthe action taken by the courts against
OL,10,Fthese individuals.
OL,12,F"Greater Manchester Police have put
OL,13,Frestrictions in place for this reverse
OL,14,Ffixture, to reduce the risk of further
OL,15,Fdisorder. The away allocation for this
OL,16,Fmatch is sold out. If you do not have
OL,17,Fa ticket for the fixture, please do
OL,18,Fnot travel into Oldham. Any away fans
OL,19,Fwho have purchased tickets in the home
OL,20,Fstands will be removed from the ground.
